                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <h4><b>FREE SHIPPING</b></h4><br>
                    <p>
                        STANDARD SHIPPING IS FREE ON ALL US IF YOU SPEND US$100.- OR MORE.<br>
                        DURING HIGH VOLUME PERIODS, EXPEDITED SHIPPING MAY NOT BE AVAILABLE.<br><br>
                    </p>

                    <h4><b>DOMESTIC</b></h4><br>
                    <p>
                        FOR DOMESTIC SHIPPING, WE OFFER STANDARD AND EXPEDITED SHIPPING. STANDARD SHIPPING TIMES REQUIRE APPROXIMATELY 5-8 BUSINESS DAYS TO DELIVER FROM THE DATE YOUR ITEM(S) IS PURCHASED AND COSTS $8.95 PER EACH UNIT. EXPEDITED SHIPPING REQUIRES APPROXIMATELY 2-3 BUSINESS DAYS TO DELIVER FROM THE DATE OF YOUR ITEM(S) IS PURCHASED AND COSTS $19.75 PER EACH UNITS. <br><br>
                    </p>

                    <h4><b>RETURNS</b></h4><br>
                    <p>
                        CLOVERUNIFORMS.COM OFFERS RETURNS UNDER THE CONDITIONS THAT THE REQUEST WAS MADE WITHIN 2 WEEKS OF THE PURCHASE DATE FOR THE ITEMS HAVE NOT BEEN DAMAGED, SOILED, WASHED, ALTERED OR WORN. ALL OF THE ORIGINAL LABELS AND TAGS MUST STILL BE ATTACHED. WE APOLOGIZE BUT WE DO NOT OFFER ANY RETURNS ON SPECIAL EMBORIDERED ITEMS. <br>
                        ALL ITEMS MARKED AS "FINAL SALE" CANNOT BE RETURNED.<br><br>
                    </p>

                    <h4><b>INITIATE A RETURN</b></h4><br>
                    <p>
                        TO BEGIN PLEASE SUBMIT AN EMAIL, INCLUDING YOUR ORDER NUMBER,ITEM NAME,COLOR AND THE PARTICULAR ITEM(S) YOU WOULD LIKE TO RETURN FROM YOUR PURCHASE TO CS@CLOVERUNIFORMS.COM <br>
                        ONE OF OUR REPRESENTATIVES WILL RESPOND TO YOUR REQUEST TYPICALLY BETWEEN 1-5 BUSINESS DAYS AND PROVIDE YOU WITH A RETURN SHIPPING LABEL THROUGH EMAIL, WHICH YOU CAN THEN USE TO RETURN THE PACKAGE TO OUR RETURN FACILITY. THE CORRESPONDING SHIPPER  WILL FOUND ON YOUR LABEL (USPS, FEDEX OR UPS). <br>
                        UPON RECEIPT OF YOUR RETURNS, YOU WILL BE PROVIDED WITH AN EMAIL CONFIRMATION.  THE REFUND AMOUNT WILL BE ISSUED TO THE SAME PAYMENT METHOD YOU USED FOR THE ORIGINAL PURCHASE, MINUS THE COST OF RETURN SHIPPING (US$8.95). PLEASE ALLOW FOR APPROXIMATELY 7-10 BUSINESS DAYS AFTER RECEIPT OF YOUR ITEMS FOR YOUR REFUND TO BE PROCESSED. <br>
                        IF YOU ENCOUNTER ANY DIFFICULTIES, PLEASE CONTACT US AT CS@CLOVERUNIFORMS.COM. <br>
                        THANK YOU!<br><br><br><br>

                    </p>


                </div>
